channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: DeSantis: We Will Conduct Our OWN Investigation Into 2nd Trump Assassination Attempt, Thank You Very Much
Tammy Baldwin faces conflict of interest concerns over partner's Wall Street gig
item.description: Baldwin is being criticized for not disclosing her partner's assets or clients because they are unmarried despite purchasing a home together.

item.title: Biden: Secret Service to Get 'Every Resource' to Protect Trump
item.description: Following the assassination attempt on former President Donald Trump at his Trump International Golf Club in West Palm Beach, Florida, on Sunday, President Joe Biden posted on X that the Secret Service would get "every resource" to protect the Republican nominee.

item.title: The Background on the Alleged Suspect in New Trump Assassination Attempt Is Something Else
‘Auto Workers for Trump’ leader says thousands poised to break from Dems over green policies, job-killing regs
item.description: Auto Workers for Trump founder Brian Pannebecker gave a wide-ranging interview to Fox News Digital, along with Rep. John James, R-Mich., who runs a company in the automotive sector.

item.title: Vance: I'm Glad Trump's Safe
item.description: Former President Donald Trump's running mate J.D. Vance expressed relief on Sunday, taking to X to write he's glad the Republican nominee is safe.

item.title: 'Doom Pixie' Greta Thunberg Wins Antisemite of the Week Award
Apache tribe takes fight with feds over sacred land to Supreme Court
item.description: An Apache tribe in Arizona is taking a fight with the federal government and copper producers over sacred land to the Supreme Court.

item.title: Guiliani to Newsmax: Would-Be Shooter Had to Study Trump International
item.description: The man who was arrested for a suspected assassination attempt on Former President Donald Trump at Trump International Golf Club Sunday had to have studied the course to know exactly where to get access and a clear line of sight, former New York City Mayor Rudolph Giuliani told Newsmax.

item.title: HOT TAKES: Left and Liberal Media Shame Themselves Over Second Trump Assassination Attempt
Ryan Routh, armed man arrested at Trump golf course, posted prolifically about Trump, politics
item.description: The armed man arrested at Trump International Golf Club, Ryan Wesley Routh, prolifically posted about politics on social media, and has dozens of arrests, documents show.

item.title: Ric Grenell to Newsmax: Bureaucrats Permit Trump's Endangerment
item.description: We may be talking about a "funeral" if the Washington bureaucrats keep former President Donald Trump from being granted adequate protection, Ric Grenell, former acting director of national intelligence in the Trump administration, told Newsmax.

item.title: Harris Surrogate Can't Answer Question When ABC News Presses on Kamala Debate Claim on US Military
Florida Gov. DeSantis says state will conduct investigation into second Trump assassination attempt
item.description: Florida Gov. Ron DeSantis announced that his state will conduct an independent investigation into the second attempted assassination of former President Trump.

item.title: Marino, Morgan: Secret Service Needs More Resources
item.description: The Secret Service will come under intensified scrutiny and criticism following a second assassination attempt of former President Donald Trump on Sunday, two former federal law officials told Newsmax.
